data.description: Sweet, canal front home that's totally fenced and well maintained in desirable Cudjoe Key that's ready for some new owners.  Good boating canal, very clean with a bubbler and easy access across Cudjoe Bay out to the Ocean or Gulf. Situated on a 7500 sq foot lot, this house includes 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a beautiful kitchen with SS appliances, bar, dining area, separate laundry room with large sink, impact doors and windows, metal roof, hardi-plank siding, trex decking, aluminum rails, built in 2017 and ready for a buyer to start enjoying the Keys life.  Step out the back patio door and down the stairs to enjoy the tropical tiki hut, 30' concrete dock, and a happy hour deck at the end of the canal for entertaining. Don't be surprised if you see a small porpoise come down that canal. Great neighborhood and Cudjoe Key offers some of the best restaurants in the Keys. Located at MM23 making it a short trip to all the nightlife that Key West has to offer. This one won't last so don't wait.
